717957f-a.title: Manhattan: Avenue C - 13th Street (East)
717957f-a.text:
213 and 223-229 Ave. C, west side, north from East 13th to 14th
Streets, showing a garage and a Vacant lot where three 5-story tenements
(Nos. 215 to 219) stood. The large 6-story apartment house (No. 223.229)
also bears Nos. 644-652 East 14th Street.
June 1, 1937.
P. L. Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.
